eruniface_104uxv1665703194681.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uxv1665703194681.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uxv1665703194681.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uxv1665703194681\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get dynamic information about a client registered with the Uniface Router.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__topic_d135083e1_d135084e1_d135085e1\">\n<p class=\"lines\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__lines_vbd_mxd_gwb\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">operation GET_CLIENT_DYN</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">params</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">Host</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C256)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  numeric</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">PID</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (I4)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  boolean</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">UpdateStatic</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: OUT ; (B2)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  entity URCLIENTD.UROUTMON : OUT</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">endparams</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__section_f3l_sxd_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d404791e95\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__ul_fmm_xxd_gwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Host</var>—client’s host name (from the URCLIENTS entity). Mandatory. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PID</var>—client’s process ID. Mandatory. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UpdateStatic</var>—specifies whether the last returned static clients view\n          should be updated (TRUE) or not (FALSE). </li>\n<li class=\"li\">URCLIENTD.UROUTMON—single occurrence of entity URCLIENTD.UROUTMON, containing client\n          information. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">URCLIENTD.UROUTMON entity</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">Fieldname</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">Packing Code</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">host</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">C256</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Client's host / IP address: primary key field 1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">pid</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Client's process ID: primary key field 2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">idle</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Ticks idle</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">idlepercent</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">I1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Percentage idle</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">busy</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Ticks busy</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">busypercent</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">I1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Percentage busy</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">wait</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Ticks wait</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">waitpercent</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">I1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Percentage wait</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">state</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">C1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">B</code> = busy, <code class=\"ph codeph\">I</code>=idle, <code class=\"ph codeph\">W</code>=wait\n                </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">srvust</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">C20</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Current or last server's UST</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">srvustque</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">I2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Position in server UST wait queue</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">srvid</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Current or last server's server ID</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">srvidque</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__2\">I2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uxv1665703194681__table_w5421ab1b5b3b5_w5422ab1b5b3_w5423ab1b5_w5424ab1__entry__4\">Position in server ID wait queue</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__section_h2s_5b2_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d404791e409\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">If successful, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to the number (zero or 1) of returned\n        URCLIENTD occurrences. A return of zero must be considered an error and a reason to update\n        the static clients view if a host name and process ID were supplied from it. For more\n        information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"man1665703194313.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/man1665703194313.html\" title=\"Get static information about clients registered with the Uniface Router.\">GET_CLIENTS</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Otherwise, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qln1665702528769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qln1665702528769.html#qln1665702528769__section_fbt_4d2_gwb\">Return Codes</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__section_pmd_c22_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d404791e435\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uxv1665703194681__section_q1j_d22_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d404791e444\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">GET_CLIENT_DYN</span> operation gets dynamic information about a\n                client, identified by its host name and process ID, that is registered with the\n                Uniface Router.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532897\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532897\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "GET_CLIENT_DYN Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 21, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get dynamic information about a client registered with the Uniface Router. operation GET_CLIENT_DYN params string Host : IN ; (C256) numeric PID : IN ; (I4) boolean UpdateStatic : OUT ; (B2) entity URCLIENTD.UROUTMON : OUT endparams Parameters Host —client’s host name (from the URCLIENTS entity). Mandatory. PID —client’s process ID. Mandatory. UpdateStatic —specifies whether the last returned static clients view should be updated (TRUE) or not (FALSE). URCLIENTD.UROUTMON—single occurrence of entity URCLIENTD.UROUTMON, containing client information. Table 1. URCLIENTD.UROUTMON entity Fieldname Packing Code Data Type Description host C256 String Client's host / IP address: primary key field 1 pid I4 Numeric Client's process ID: primary key field 2 idle I4 Numeric Ticks idle idlepercent I1 Numeric Percentage idle busy I4 Numeric Ticks busy busypercent I1 Numeric Percentage busy wait I4 Numeric Ticks wait waitpercent I1 Numeric Percentage wait state C1 String B = busy, I =idle, W =wait srvust C20 String Current or last server's UST srvustque I2 Numeric Position in server UST wait queue srvid I4 Numeric Current or last server's server ID srvidque I2 Numeric Position in server ID wait queue Return Values If successful, $status is set to the number (zero or 1) of returned URCLIENTD occurrences. A return of zero must be considered an error and a reason to update the static clients view if a host name and process ID were supplied from it. For more information, see GET_CLIENTS . Otherwise, see Return Codes . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The GET_CLIENT_DYN operation gets dynamic information about a client, identified by its host name and process ID, that is registered with the Uniface Router. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}